Package ru.rsreu.kuznecovsokolov12.datalayer.data

Class AbstractEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.rsreu.kuznecovsokolov12.datalayer.data.AbstractEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeletedMessage, Message, MessageAttaching, Role, RoleAssigment, RoleGroup, Sanction, SanctionType, Setting, Team, TeamInteract, TeamInteractType, User
    public abstract class AbstractEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    The AbstractEntity class serves as a superclass for all entity classes related to database tables. It contains a single attribute, id, which uniquely identifies the entity in the database.

    This abstract class provides methods for getting and setting the id attribute, as well as implementing equals and hashCode methods based on the id for proper comparison and hashing in collections.
